104
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,480
How could I

105
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,680
not want to marry you?

106
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,370
It's just that I thought

107
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,280
my situation was too dangerous,

108
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:22,340
and I was afraid of dragging you down.

109
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,640
No matter how dangerous, didn't we

110
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,570
