111
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,690
As long as you are sincere to me.

112
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,320
Of course I am.

113
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,740
I, Chen Jiadong, swear

114
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,880
